<section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div
    class="
      gap-16
      items-center
      py-8
      px-4
      mx-auto
      max-w-screen-xl
      lg:grid
      lg:grid-cols-2
      lg:py-16
      lg:px-6
    "
  >
    <div class="font-light text-gray-500 sm:text-lg dark:text-gray-400">
      <h2
        class="
          mb-4
          text-4xl
          tracking-tight
          font-extrabold
          text-gray-900
          dark:text-white
        "
      >Steps to book a property</h2>
      <ul>
        <li class="mb-4">1. signup as guest</li>
        <li class="mb-4">2. Browse our vast collection of properties</li>
        <li class="mb-4">3. Click on rerserve buton</li>
        <li class="mb-4">4. Complete the reservation form and submit the booking request</li>
        <li class="mb-4">5. verify your My bookings section and check if your request was approved or declined</li>
        <li class="mb-4">6. If your booking request was approved wait until the checkin day and just enjoy</li>
        <li class="mb-4">7. If your booking request was declined, most likely the host provided a reason. Learn form that reason and improve your next request.</li>
        <li class="mb-4">8. After your first stay don't forget to add a review. Check My bookings section, look for your target booking and click on add review button. Add your rating and leave a message.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4">If this guide is no helpful enough click <%= link_to contact_path do %> <span class="font-semibold">here</span> <% end %> to send us a message and we will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-8">
      <%= image_tag "about_us_apartment", class: "w-full rounded-lg" %>
      <%= image_tag "about_us_house", class: "mt-4 w-full lg:mt-10 rounded-lg" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
